parameters:
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>What's with this parking lot? It's exclusively for
executives but it's unnecessarily spacious.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>And the employee parking costs 500 yen per hour... Are they
even managing it properly?
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Wow! A cat...? Why is there a cat here...?

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Now that I think about it... there was a day when a cat
scratched an executive's car and someone's job evaluation
got nullified.
\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>Could it be you who did that?

\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>Huh? What's this... a bowl and food for a cat? Is someone
feeding them here?

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Who on earth...? They'd be in big trouble if they got
caught...
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>(This is... a human voice, isn't it?)
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>(Eh? Se-senpai? What are they doing over there...)
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>(So, it was senpai who's been feeding the cats here...)
\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>Oh, it's you, Saki. You're not slacking off, are you?

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>Well... Saki wouldn't just abandon her work to slack off.
You don't have the guts for that.
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Is that supposed to be a compliment...?

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Of course. I've actually given you good evaluations. But
still, I've shown you something I shouldn't have...
\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>Yes. I've been feeding the cats here.
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Why would you do such a thing!?

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>But cats are noisy! They mess up the surroundings and damage
cars...

\bustMsgExp[2, 2]\nc<Senpai>That's the best part. Anyway, regular employees can't park
here.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>That's not the point, what if you get caught... The cars
have drive recorders and all...

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>Our company's cars don't have such things. Who do you think
would be in big trouble if the company's internal affairs
were exposed?

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>In the end, as long as you keep quiet, there won't be any
problems. You won't tell anyone else, right?

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Yes, well... It would be sad if senpai got sent away on
forced dispatch because of something like this.
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>(Besides, senpai is trusted much more than I am...)

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Is that the right phrase to use here? Well, whatever. Thank
you.
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Please don't sulk over something like that!
